381
00:35:27,430 --> 00:35:28,860
Rồi đó.

382
00:35:28,860 --> 00:35:31,190
Ổn rồi đấy.

383
00:35:32,100 --> 00:35:34,030
Vanessa Shelly.

384
00:35:34,860 --> 00:35:36,290
Mike.

385
00:35:36,300 --> 00:35:38,560
